---
import MainLayout from '@layouts/MainLayout.astro';
---

<MainLayout
  title="Política de Privacidad"
  description="Política de privacidad de Sostenibilidad y Energía DIY. Información sobre cómo recopilamos, usamos y protegemos tus datos personales.">

  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-50 to-indigo-100 py-16">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center">
        <div class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-16 h-16 bg-blue-100 rounded-full mb-6">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-blue-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 15v2m-6 4h12a2 2 0 002-2v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2zm10-10V7a4 4 0 00-8 0v4h8z"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Política de Privacidad</h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          Tu privacidad es importante para nosotros. Conoce cómo protegemos y utilizamos tu información.
        </p>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mt-4">Última actualización: Marzo 2026</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Content -->
  <section class="py-16">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-xl p-8 md:p-12">
        <div class="space-y-8">
          <!-- Información General -->
          <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-50 to-indigo-50 rounded-xl p-6 border-l-4 border-blue-500">
            <div class="flex items-start space-x-4">
              <div class="flex-shrink-0">
                <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-blue-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
                  <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-blue-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 16h-1v-4h-1m1-4h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
                  </svg>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">1. Información General</h2>
                <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
                  En Sostenibilidad y Energía DIY nos comprometemos a proteger tu privacidad y tus datos personales.
                  Esta política de privacidad explica cómo recopilamos, usamos, almacenamos y protegemos tu información
                  cuando utilizas nuestro sitio web.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Datos que Recopilamos -->
          <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-xl p-6 shadow-sm">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6 flex items-center">
              <span class="w-8 h-8 bg-green-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mr-3">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12h6m-6 4h6m2 5H7a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h5.586a1 1 0 01.707.293l5.414 5.414a1 1 0 01.293.707V19a2 2 0 01-2 2z"></path>
                </svg>
              </span>
              2. Datos que Recopilamos
            </h2>

            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
              <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-4">
                <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3 flex items-center">
                  <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-blue-500 mr-2" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                    <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                  </svg>
                  Datos proporcionados voluntariamente
                </h3>
                <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
                  <li class="flex items-start">
                    <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-blue-500 rounded-full mt-2 mr-3 flex-shrink-0"></span>
                    Información de contacto cuando nos contactas
                  </li>
                  <li class="flex items-start">
                    <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-blue-500 rounded-full mt-2 mr-3 flex-shrink-0"></span>
                    Datos de formularios de calculadoras
                  </li>
                  <li class="flex items-start">
                    <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-blue-500 rounded-full mt-2 mr-3 flex-shrink-0"></span>
                    Comentarios y consultas enviadas
                  </li>
                </ul>
              </div>

              <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-4">
                <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3 flex items-center">
                  <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-purple-500 mr-2" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                    <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M3 4a1 1 0 011-1h12a1 1 0 110 2H4a1 1 0 01-1-1zm0 4a1 1 0 011-1h12a1 1 0 110 2H4a1 1 0 01-1-1zm0 4a1 1 0 011-1h12a1 1 0 110 2H4a1 1 0 01-1-1z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                  </svg>
                  Datos recopilados automáticamente
                </h3>
                <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
                  <li class="flex items-start">
                    <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-purple-500 rounded-full mt-2 mr-3 flex-shrink-0"></span>
                    Dirección IP y datos de navegación
                  </li>
                  <li class="flex items-start">
                    <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-purple-500 rounded-full mt-2 mr-3 flex-shrink-0"></span>
                    Cookies y tecnologías similares
                  </li>
                  <li class="flex items-start">
                    <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-purple-500 rounded-full mt-2 mr-3 flex-shrink-0"></span>
                    Información del dispositivo y navegador
                  </li>
                  <li class="flex items-start">
                    <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-purple-500 rounded-full mt-2 mr-3 flex-shrink-0"></span>
                    Datos de uso del sitio web
                  </li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Uso de los Datos -->
          <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-xl p-6 shadow-sm">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6 flex items-center">
              <span class="w-8 h-8 bg-amber-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mr-3">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-amber-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2h8a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2h-2M9 5a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2M9 5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2"></path>
                </svg>
              </span>
              3. Uso de los Datos
            </h2>
            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">Utilizamos tus datos para:</p>
            <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-3">
              <div class="flex items-start space-x-3">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                </svg>
                <span class="text-gray-700">Proporcionar y mejorar nuestros servicios</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-start space-x-3">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                </svg>
                <span class="text-gray-700">Responder a tus consultas e inquietudes</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-start space-x-3">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                </svg>
                <span class="text-gray-700">Enviar información relevante sobre energía solar</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-start space-x-3">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                </svg>
                <span class="text-gray-700">Analizar el uso del sitio para mejoras</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Cookies -->
          <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-50 to-pink-50 rounded-xl p-6 border-l-4 border-purple-500">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4 flex items-center">
              <span class="w-8 h-8 bg-purple-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mr-3">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-purple-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M21 12a9 9 0 01-9 9m9-9a9 9 0 00-9-9m9 9H3m9 9v-9m0-9v9"></path>
                </svg>
              </span>
              4. Cookies y Tecnologías Similares
            </h2>
            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
              Utilizamos cookies para mejorar tu experiencia en nuestro sitio. Para más información,
              consulta nuestra <a href="/politica-cookies" class="text-purple-600 hover:text-purple-800 font-medium underline">Política de Cookies</a>.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Seguridad -->
          <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-green-50 to-emerald-50 rounded-xl p-6 border-l-4 border-green-500">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4 flex items-center">
              <span class="w-8 h-8 bg-green-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mr-3">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z"></path>
                </svg>
              </span>
              5. Seguridad de los Datos
            </h2>
            <p class="text-gray-700">
              Implementamos medidas de seguridad técnicas y organizativas apropiadas para proteger
              tus datos personales contra pérdida, uso indebido o acceso no autorizado.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Tus Derechos -->
          <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-xl p-6 shadow-sm">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6 flex items-center">
              <span class="w-8 h-8 bg-indigo-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mr-3">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-indigo-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm6 3a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM7 10a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0z"></path>
                </svg>
              </span>
              6. Tus Derechos
            </h2>
            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">Tienes derecho a:</p>
            <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-3">
              <div class="flex items-start space-x-3">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-500 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                </svg>
                <span class="text-gray-700">Acceder a tus datos personales</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-start space-x-3">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-500 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                </svg>
                <span class="text-gray-700">Rectificar datos inexactos</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-start space-x-3">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-500 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                </svg>
                <span class="text-gray-700">Solicitar la eliminación de tus datos</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-start space-x-3">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-500 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                </svg>
                <span class="text-gray-700">Oponerte al procesamiento</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Contacto -->
          <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-gray-50 to-slate-50 rounded-xl p-6 border border-gray-200">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4 flex items-center">
              <span class="w-8 h-8 bg-gray-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mr-3">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-gray-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 8l7.89 4.26a2 2 0 002.22 0L21 8M5 19h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z"></path>
                </svg>
              </span>
              Contacto
            </h2>
            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
              Si tienes preguntas sobre esta política de privacidad, puedes contactarnos:
            </p>
            <div class="space-y-2">
              <p class="flex items-center text-gray-700">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-gray-500 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 8l7.89 4.26a2 2 0 002.22 0L21 8M5 19h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z"></path>
                </svg>
                Email: privacidad@sostenibilidad-energia-diy.com
              </p>
              <p class="flex items-center text-gray-700">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-gray-500 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M21 12a9 9 0 01-9 9m9-9a9 9 0 00-9-9m9 9H3m9 9v-9m0-9v9"></path>
                </svg>
                Formulario de contacto en nuestro sitio web
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</MainLayout>